    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a dependable daily driver or a solid base for a restoration project. The exterior shows some expected signs of age, including noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with several small dings and scratches. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits some wear on the upholstery and a few cracked trim pieces. Mechanically, it runs well, though it may benefit from a tune-up and some minor maintenance in the near future. It is a honest car that reflects its history and is priced accordingly.",
