    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with a ton of love? This beauty is in wonderful shape and drives like an absolute dream! It\u2019s been my trusty companion for a while now, and it has never let me down. It's super clean, runs smoothly, and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you. Whether you're heading out on a road trip or just zipping around town, you're going to feel great behind the wheel. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six engine. This A80 chassis remains a formidable performer, retaining its factory sequential twin-turbochargers and the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The drivetrain delivers linear power through a Torsen limited-slip differential, while the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension provides precise turn-in and high-speed stability. Recent maintenance includes a full timing belt service and inspection of the vacuum lines for the sequential boost control system. Though it shows minor cosmetic signs of its heritage, the compression across all cylinders is within spec, and the gear synchronization remains crisp. A true driver\u2019s example of JDM engineering excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
