    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It runs beautifully, looks great, and is just waiting for someone to take it on a new adventure! If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to help you get behind the wheel!",
      "price": 28900.0,
