      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 high-revving inline-six. This example is mechanically robust, with the Double VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein adjustable coilovers, providing exceptional turn-in and lateral stability. While showing minor patina consistent with its age, the car maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Shod in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this M3 is dialed for the enthusiast who values tactile feedback and high-revving naturally aspirated performance.",
